Package: cowgreeting
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, cowsay, bash | dash
Description: Enhanced time-aware greeting system with cowsay
 CowGreeting is cowhello on steroids - an enhanced shell script
 that provides personalized, time-aware greetings using the cowsay utility.
 .
 Features:
  * Time-aware greetings (morning/afternoon/evening)
  * Personalized with system username
  * Customizable date and time formats
  * Plugin system for extensibility
  * Cross-shell compatible (bash, zsh)
  * Configurable via ~/.config/cowgreeting/greetcow.conf
 .
 Perfect for adding personality to your shell login or .bashrc/.zshrc files. 